The harmony line is not aggro reduction. And while the memblur line is technically aggro reduction, it can cause a lot more problems than it solves in a fight, so it really doesn't count either.<br>
<br>
The only actual classes that have personal aggro reduction are Rogues (evade and escape), Wizards (Concussion), Rangers (jolt), and Bards (escape). Personal aggro reduction is what is useful in fights, memblur is much too situational.<br>
